HEADWORD: Glim
<hw>Glim</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Brightness;
splendor.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A light or candle.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>
<rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Douse the glim</b></col>, <cd>put out the light.</cd>
<mark>[Slang]</mark></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glimmer</ent>⟦br⟧
